{"tid":1590201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"929全人類做舉旗撚","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:41:38.000Z","uid":243666,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a60dd0a797dd58411369c5b95f78342812466a5a","tid":1590201,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.29要爭取國際focus</span><br />\n呢排國際傳媒日日報打架報到悶<br />\n所以我哋要做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舉旗撚</span></span><br />\n個畫面好睇 而且有新鮮感<br />\n舉旗人數要夠多 最好超過10萬人 <br />\n而我哋要舉返<span style=\"color: gold;\">自己嘅旗</span> 如 黑色區旗/自由鳥<br />\n<br />\n第一 自己嘅旗有歸屬感 凝聚翻香港人<br />\n<br />\n第二 手足為香港而戰並非其他國家<br />\n所以9.29舉美國舉略有不妥<br />\n<br />\n第三 多次舉美國旗會引起外國人反感<br />\n<br />\n另外 格離post話有日本人想幫手<br />\n我建議9.29夾埋日本 台灣 組織一次全球反共大遊行"},{"pid":"ab69f253935ab8139e7af82ad24b5a1e04cf72bb","tid":1590201,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"【10.1民陣遊行】十萬護旗手揮舞美國國旗，擁抱美帝嘅民主！自由！正義！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590183</a>"},{"pid":"efac8ed32a2e27bcb9c8d7ce8cb778918cef55f2","tid":1590201,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"ff358b40dd94c8010b4705eaefef9df77e493204","tid":1590201,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"9215a199e6cd40c815b43fec75fea5592f69bb09","tid":1590201,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6546bf1a67dd57a943b05